  "about": {
    "details": "<p>Incorporated in July 2005, Varyaa Creations Limited deals in wholesale trading of gold, silver, precious stones, and semi-precious stones.</p>\n<p>The product portfolio includes Necklaces, Earrings, Tops, Rings, Bracelets, Bangles, Gemstones, Diamonds, Lab-grown diamonds, and Pearls. The company also create custom-made jewellery based on customers' requirements.</p>\n<p>The portfolio offers customers various jewellery designs for all occasions and price points.</p>\n<p>As of 31st March 2024, the company employs 8 people in various departments.</p>"
  },
